text.title: BINNENGEKOMEN.
text.p: TEXEL, 16 Sept.; Cardenas Packet, Fraay, Havana. - Ivanhoe, S., Leith. - Hart, Cloak, Newcastle. - Bermuda, Hales, id. - Maria, Brydo, Wyburg.
